title: OMG - One More Goddess
description: Real and Raunchy - OMG is a high flying, transformational adventure.Meet Jessica - a fresh faced and fancy free Aussie, about to fulfil the biggest dream of her young life, jetting off to the USA on her own.While that in itself is nothing out of the ordinary - it s all about to change.Fate has a different plan for her - in the form of Diego and Samantha who open up an entirely new, sexy world that takes her to an extraordinary high.It all appears too good to be true and Jessica feels great - but is this world of sunshine and lollipops really just dildos and blow jobs?Are you ready to fly Angel Air?Welcome aboard..."
author: Tony  Marino
